{"tid":2246707,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[柏傲莊] 慈母資助首期　海歸派牙醫擬與姐弟共購3伙","createTime":"2020-10-17T09:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T10:22:15.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c75b67e772ea1e18080ee7f5f974a1b220f8baa0","tid":2246707,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T09:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201017/394149384373145600620137.jpeg/WD787JX9oQ17ITvOP45s2t3VDwhbbxt7G9_e-Rvf3vk?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201017%2F394149384373145600620137.jpeg%2FWD787JX9oQ17ITvOP45s2t3VDwhbbxt7G9_e-Rvf3vk%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=69abf004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新世界發展（0017）與港鐵（0066）旗下的大圍站柏傲莊 I 本周六、日分兩輪銷售共391伙。今日為大手客時段，仍有多名準買家到場，準備選購合適單位，在美國擔任牙醫多年的鄭小姐便是其中之一。<span class=\"red\">她指出在母親支持下，姐弟3人計劃選購3伙，包括最少1個三房單位。<br />\n</span><br />\n鄭小姐表示一家人本身都住馬鞍山，選擇該項目亦因對附近一帶的熟悉，又有家人又在香港城市大學工作，交通方便，可以互相照應。鄭小姐表示，打算與姐姐，弟弟共購3個單位，最少會揀一個三房單位。<br />\n<br />\n鄭小姐表示，今次入市獲母親出手相助，幫助大家支付首期，各人再自行供樓。剛放假回港的她指出，未來打算回港工作<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201017/394095037681635328619027.jpeg/cft7bxVtkUkupqwWy9ypVUo7DE7MNrikslJpWbJSaVk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201017%2F394095037681635328619027.jpeg%2Fcft7bxVtkUkupqwWy9ypVUo7DE7MNrikslJpWbJSaVk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a2e07040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭小姐指，自己在美國亦擁有物業，對樓市地產方面亦感興趣，因此有意在香港置業。由於剛回港放假，對香港樓市不太熟悉，有賴家人提供意見。"},{"pid":"e96487fc4c7197715447990e080c28b936edb5ea","tid":2246707,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"岩架啦買多兩棟"},{"pid":"8833f3b3c6f519df2ad0bb3365121c25364f0550","tid":2246707,"uid":278906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T09:52:37.000Z","msg":"東華義莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ef5007d4aa6d646c42d1e1add9c80cf8564dc0","tid":2246707,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"平到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抽中當中六合彩"}]}